item.title: AWS SageMaker Deep Dive
item.description: This post consist of the notes that are based on the series of AWS SageMaker videos provided by Amazon Web Services Amazon SageMaker Technical Deep Dive Series. Fully-Managed Notebook Instances with Amazon SageMaker Create your Notebook Instance: Pick the right family: t - tiny < m, c - computed optimized, p - GPU Pick the right size: From medium to very very large. Pick the right version: ml.t3.medium: 3 means the latest version in the T family There are ~200 example notebooks in SageMaker Notebook, definitely try them out.
